<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Activation - Bright Horizon Institute</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #fff;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff4e00;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #ff4e00;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .warning {
            color: red;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ff4e00;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="company-name">Bright Horizon Institute</div>
        <h1>Welcome, <%= user.name %>!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for registering in our Learning Management System.</p>
        <p>Your account activation code is:</p>
        <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
        <p class="warning">⚠ Please enter this code in your activation page within next 5 mins</p>
        <p>Please enter this code in the app to activate your account.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any issues, feel free to contact us at  
               <a href="mailto:training@brighthorizoninstitute.com">training@brighthorizoninstitute.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Bright Horizon Institute. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
